Datas.Name: Splitter
Datas.Describe: It is well known as a powerful role in the car industry. Its cutting blades are very sharp and can cut most of the metal.

Datas.Name: Marauder
Datas.Describe: The Digital World's best sellers. Its equipments are very powerful, it can destroy various obstacles and is unimpeded in the Digital World.

Datas.Name: Behemoth
Datas.Describe: Unknown existence in the digital world, weak digimons will be controlled by it if gets on, and keeps running to death. Only digimons with real power can own this power.

Datas.Name: Barrier impact
Datas.Describe: There is a rumor that it is a very powerful car in the Digital World . Its powerful impact can break through any defense, including city walls. Once you have this power, you can do anything.

Datas.Name: Frontline assault
Datas.Describe: A sign for victory on the battlefields of the digital world. The ability to strike the first line of enemy forces on the battlefield is beyond imagination. Having this grants the courage to win.

Datas.Name: Soul Burst
Datas.Describe: All the time bustling around the Digital World, but due to absorbing too many digital souls from various places, souls are always bursting while walking. Its power is invincible.

Datas.Name: Energy Reduction
Datas.Describe: It is said that it was created to maintain the energy balance of the digital world, to absorb energies that are too powerful. It usually appears in places where energy has no contraint and digimons roam uncontrolled and rampage.

Datas.Name: Edge Conquer
Datas.Describe: It is always used to run on the edge of the digital worldï¼Œ and expel the invasion of anomalous data.  It is acts as if it is a guardian of the digital world. Its own strength is extremely strong.

Datas.Name: Space Collapse
Datas.Describe: A car that can travel freely in the digital world and other spaces. Due to an accident in space shuttle, it has the ability to open the space at any time and release its own enormous energy.

Datas.Name: Power Decomposition
Datas.Describe: Good at decomposing all kinds of data, if you encounter it in the digital world, you can only try to escape. Once something is locked and hit, it will be broken down immediately.

Datas.Name: Energy Liberation
Datas.Describe: The mount was made by a large number of data. Its huge data is concentrated on its metal body. In battle, it can release concentrated energy and cause great harm.

Datas.Name: Soul Reorganization
Datas.Describe: It can be said that it is an ambulance in the digital world. The data it carries is used for repair purposes.  The wonderful thing is that there are 120 groups of data that can be loaded, so some people speculate that there are certain links with certain rules from the human world.

Datas.Name: Holy Light Swirl
Datas.Describe: The strongest mount in the field of angels, the light that it usually shines, is full of harmony. Once in battle, it represents absolute justice.

Datas.Name: Fast Aurora
Datas.Describe: The color of the car body is like an aurora that keeps changing, but what is not visible on the surface is the magnetic field it is emitting.  It can walk freely and change the direction of the target during the battle.

Datas.Name: Bonfire Burning
Datas.Describe: It is the super Bomber of the Digital World.  The name is because that once it appears on the battlefield, it will overwhelm the entire battlefield with fire. It is such an extremely horrible existence.

Datas.Name: Ice Crystal
Datas.Describe: It is the only frozen mount in the digital world, and it use cryogenic guns equipped on both sides of the car body to attack .  As soon as you are slightly close to it, the gas emitted will freeze you.

Datas.Name: King Power
Datas.Describe: It is the legend of the digital world. Its whole body is made of digital metal, and energy ball it releases has the ability to draw the target into different space. It is said that only the real king can control it.

Datas.Name: Thunder Master
Datas.Describe: As the fire bursts, its anger runs strong, and the grass does not grow, and just like the Thunder, it leaves no trace of life.

Datas.Name: Light Speed
Datas.Describe: It is known as the fastest mount in the digital world, it is capable of moving at the speed of light. Its specialty is its hard metal body built with digital metal that can hit targets with high speed.

Datas.Name: Dark Riot
Datas.Describe: It is a super dark mount that made by the dark digital beast with the technology stolen by Steel Empire.  Its outbreak of darkness can reach the level of the devil.
